    "description": "探访世界上最大的飞机‘墓地’，深入广袤的沙漠，那里遍布着飞机的残骸。成百上千吨的钢铁和废弃电子设备正静候你的发掘。拆解飞机，通过废品赚取金钱，并完成雇主交付的任务！在切割、敲打、拆解并组装新飞机的过程中，不断发展壮大你的业务规模！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拆除</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/e3395137eebde52ee6d21b7b7c633ddd.poster.avif?t=1765312196\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/e3395137eebde52ee6d21b7b7c633ddd.webm?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/e3395137eebde52ee6d21b7b7c633ddd.mp4?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>挥刀切割飞机机身，拆解飞机骨架，搜寻宝贵的部件，如飞行员座舱，它们将助你完成任务。利用升降设备，轻松触及飞机难以抵达的部位。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >废弃材料</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/5222b48b4ad63028fe2284ee30acf39c.poster.avif?t=1765312196\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/5222b48b4ad63028fe2284ee30acf39c.webm?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/5222b48b4ad63028fe2284ee30acf39c.mp4?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>将飞机机身和结构部件运至废品处理场进行处理。利用各式车辆进行运输，并在废品场兑换你的劳动成果，赚取丰厚金钱。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/b9e3d1956c8d1c0cb9093b4a49e96dc9.poster.avif?t=1765312196\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/b9e3d1956c8d1c0cb9093b4a49e96dc9.webm?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/b9e3d1956c8d1c0cb9093b4a49e96dc9.mp4?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的办公室即是你的大本营。在此管理订单，探索新任务。在限定的时间内完成任务，不断充实自己。通过投资新飞机，推动你的事业更上一层楼。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拆卸</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/69b7afc2246e184bc73cd57ae7a8bd67.poster.avif?t=1765312196\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/69b7afc2246e184bc73cd57ae7a8bd67.webm?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/69b7afc2246e184bc73cd57ae7a8bd67.mp4?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>挑战复杂任务，如回收发动机和珍贵电子设备。需谨记，发动机价值连城，任何轻率的举动都可能导致订单丢失，金钱付诸东流！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展你的业务</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/e73f884bb2d4725b33e10174905aebe7.poster.avif?t=1765312196\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/e73f884bb2d4725b33e10174905aebe7.webm?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128610/extras/e73f884bb2d4725b33e10174905aebe7.mp4?t=1765312196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过购买新飞机进行翻修，拓展你的业务领域。投资建设新型机库，成为飞机‘墓地’行业的佼佼者，独领风骚！",
